sizes available)</li><li><strong>Collection:</strong> Draped in Time</li></ul>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_care": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Care", "heading_column_1": "Jewelry Care", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p><strong>Enamel Rings:</strong> Remove before washing hands, swimming, or exercise. Enamel is durable but can chip on hard impacts \u2014 avoid knocking against hard surfaces. Store in the provided pouch, separate from other jewelry. Clean with a soft, dry cloth. Do not use jewelry cleaners or ultrasonic cleaners on enamel.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_shipping": {"type": "two_column_tab", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Shipping & Returns", "content_vertical_alignment": "top", "column_spacing": 48, "heading_column_1": "Made to Order", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>Every ring is handcrafted to order in NYC. The enamel process alone requires multiple firings over several days. Please allow 3\u20134 weeks for production. Free insured shipping on all orders. Signature required on delivery. You'll receive email updates during production and tracking when your piece ships.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text", "heading_column_2": "Returns & Warranty", "heading_font_class_column_2": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_2": "h3", "text_column_2": "<p>All sales are final \u2014 each piece is made specifically for you. 1-year warranty covers manufacturing defects. If your piece arrives damaged, contact us within 14 days with photos for repair or replacement.</p>", "page_for_content_column_2": "", "custom_liquid_column_2": "", "text_font_class_column_2": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_2": 100, "image_position_column_2": "above_text"}}}, "block_order": ["tab_description", "tab_details", "tab_care", "tab_shipping"], "settings": {"tab_alignment": "left", "tab_spacing": 40, "font_choice": "ff-heading", "tab_font_size": "fs-body-150", "auto_collapse_rows": false, "background_color": "", "text_color": "#000000", "enable_animation": true, "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-bottom-only"}}, "multi-column": {"type": "multi-column", "blocks": {}, "block_order": [], "disabled": true, "settings": {"title": "", "heading_tag": "h2", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-3-base", "subheading": "", "heading_alignment": "left", "content_vertical_alignment": "center", "content_background_padding": "large", "columns": "3", "column_spacing": 4, "row_spacing": 28, "column_alignment": "center", "enable_slider_mobile": false, "columns_mobile": "1", "column_spacing_mobile": 4, "row_spacing_mobile": 4, "column_alignment_mobile": "center", "background_behind_columns": false, "background_color": "#f5f3f0", "text_color": "#3d352f", "button_background_color": "#000000", "button_text_color": "#ffffff", "enable_animation": true, "divider_style": "none", "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-top-bottom"}}, "image-hero": {"type": "image-hero", "blocks": {"accent": {"type": "accent", "settings": {"accent": "DRAPED IN TIME"}}, "heading": {"type": "heading", "settings": {"title": "Coconut Clover", "heading_tag": "h2", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-display-2"}}}, "block_order": ["accent", "heading"], "settings": {"image_aspect": "custom", "desktop_height": 60, "mobile_height": 65, "focal_point": "center", "mobile_focal_poin